    public class CommandException
extends PayException
    Project: LUIS ePayment

    A CommandException and its derived classes will get thrown if a command, sent to the payment terminal, returns some error. This error is signaled by the payment terminal itself. The communication between LUIS ePayment and the payment terminal is not broken down.

    Version:
    $Revision: 1.8 $

    M. Gelfort
